title: Kabob and Tandoori Ghar
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Nepalese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Himalayan cuisine. Menu has vegetable curries, each comes with rice. The vegan suitable ones are tofu matar, aloo cauli, vegetable korma, and mixed vegetable; the other contain dairy. One of the naan bread is vegan, the others are not. Kids menu has 3 vegetarian choices.
